import { Box, Card, Grid } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const RecentProperty = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{p:5 , my:0}}>
        <Card p={10}>
           <Grid lg={4} sm={12}>
            image
           </Grid>
           <Grid lg={8} sm={12}>
            data
           </Grid>
        </Card>


    </Box>
  )
}

export default RecentProperty
